Document: CSGTorus3D
Path: godot/classes/class_csgtorus3d.rst
Summary: Creates a torus shape for use in the CSG system with performance considerations for prototyping.

Note: CSG nodes are intended for level prototyping due to significant CPU costs compared to MeshInstance3D with PrimitiveMesh. Moving CSG nodes within other CSG nodes during gameplay should be avoided because of high computational overhead.
